channel.title: Weak Assurance - Common Need [Techno]
channel.description:
Hello There!
It's my first post here in this amazing forum. Here my newest track made in Auxy :slight_smile: [https://soundcloud.com/weak-assurance/common-need](https://soundcloud.com/weak-assurance/common-need)
I was undecided about it because I still am not trusting to my personal style and inspiration. I would be honored to receive feedback and advices to improve and open to a good conversation :grimacing:
Enjoy,
Antonio R
